{"tid":427320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國在河內承建鐵路瀕臨爛尾","createTime":"2017-10-07T12:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T14:55:16.000Z","uid":51271,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"aa4d93aa2b95abf54151778c182871bbee932c42","tid":427320,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:08:53.000Z","msg":"【中國在河內承建鐵路瀕臨爛尾】<br />\n<br />\nNIKKEI Asian Review 近日報導，九年前中國承諾協助越南在河內興建的高架鐵路系統，上月取消了試行。<br />\n<br />\n當地政府回覆記者詢問時表示，由於中方仍未注入所需的2.5億美元後續資金，所以整個項目不能繼續下去。<br />\n<br />\n早於2008年，中國政府已承諾投入4億美元興建這鐵路系統，其後成本增加了超過六成，但中方一直未有投入新資金。<br />\n<br />\n報導指，工程期間亦引起當地很大爭議，工業意外頻生，河內的交通亦大受影響，河內居民多次表達了不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.nikkei.com/Politics-Economy/Economy/China-s-projects-in-Vietnam-earn-reputation-for-poor-quality-delays\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FPolitics-Economy%2FEconomy%2FChina-s-projects-in-Vietnam-earn-reputation-for-poor-quality-delays&d=1MGcE3XRFIEMBMZtt5lJC26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e024a364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asia.nikkei.com/Politics-Economy/Economy/China-s-projects-in-Vietnam-earn-reputation-for-poor-quality-delays</a>"},{"pid":"2e627d6593f4bcc4b00f2ed2256f5bf57fa3fb14","tid":427320,"uid":3117,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:10:59.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那"},{"pid":"90d41078bbeb256ff35aa0e88cdf5086c931004b","tid":427320,"uid":12449,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先兆"},{"pid":"17ce1ede93363a7f5da7c7fd080755b53c47b400","tid":427320,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T12:22:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">等睇鳩投行益新Member港豬接力！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/